data.text: @people @VancityReynolds @blakelively  the same people who hate being questioned about their relationships are the first to speculate on other's relationships. Must be so annoying to even have to give a response. #MindYourOwnBusiness
@people I hope they never break up. I always enjoy their banter and they make such cute kids!
@people This is what happens with working parents and marriage.. Can't spend as much time together alone, but I am glad they are working it out.
